'''Mhlume Airfield''' {{airport codes||FDMH}} is an [[airstrip]] serving [[Mhlume]], an agricultural town in the [[Lubombo Region]] of [[Swaziland]]. The runway is on the northwest corner of the town.
The Sikhuphe [[VOR-DME]] (Ident: '''VSK''') is located {{convert|21.7|nmi|km|1}} south of the airstrip. The Mhlume [[non-directional beacon]] (Ident: '''HL''') is located on the field.<ref>{{cite web |title=Mhlume NDB, Sikhuphe VOR |url=https://skyvector.com/?ll=-26.185,31.737&chart=301&zoom=1 |website=SkyVector Aeronautical Charts |publisher=SkyVector |accessdate=18 June 2018}}</ref>
