{{italic title}}
'''''Miel luxembourgeois de marque nationale''''' is a [[honey]] from [[Luxembourg]] that is protected under EU law with ''[[Protected geographical indications in the European Union|PDO]]'' status.{{Citation needed|date=June 2015}}

Some of the criteria for the production of this honey include that it:
*''must'' be of high quality
*may ''not'' contain any imported honey
*may ''not'' contain any additives
*''must'' have a water content of less than 20%

